# Example Applications

The project includes example applications demonstrating how to integrate Xellar-Kit:

## React + Vite Example

The [apps/react-vite/](mdc:apps/react-vite) directory contains a React application using Vite that demonstrates how to integrate Xellar-Kit in a standard React application.

Key files:
- [apps/react-vite/src/App.tsx](mdc:apps/react-vite/src/App.tsx) - Main application component
- [apps/react-vite/src/main.tsx](mdc:apps/react-vite/src/main.tsx) - Entry point with provider setup

## Next.js Example

The [apps/next-app/](mdc:apps/next-app) directory contains a Next.js application demonstrating how to integrate Xellar-Kit in a Next.js project.

Key files:
- [apps/next-app/app/page.tsx](mdc:apps/next-app/app/page.tsx) - Main page component
- [apps/next-app/app/providers.tsx](mdc:apps/next-app/app/providers.tsx) - Provider configuration
